data.description: Welcome to this half-acre, corner lot in desirable Lake Riviera! This 3 bed, 2 bath custom, contemporary style home has the potential to be  the feature property in a quiet neighborhood. Single story living and plenty of windows allow tons of natural light into all parts of the home. Stylish features include vaulted ceilings, custom stone fireplace, rear den with sliding doors and spiral staircase to your lofted second floor. With private back deck, 2-car garage, and U-shaped driveway, this home offers so much to it's new owners. 15 minute drive to the beach and conveniently close to major shopping centers and the parkway. Schedule your showing today!
